        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 74170,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Este loop <code>for</code> conta de <code>1</code> a <code>5</code>. Vamos aprender como alterá-lo para fazer um loop decrescente de <code>5</code> a <code>1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &lt; \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i++) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"5\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Counter variable",
            "id": 74172,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Primeiro, vamos mudar onde o loop começa definindo a variável de contagem para <code>5</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &lt; \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i++) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"14\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>5</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Condition",
            "id": 74173,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em seguida, vamos mudar a condição para que o loop <strong>pare</strong> quando <code>i</code> for maior que <code>0</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &gt; \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i--) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"1\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>i</code> seguido de <code>&gt;</code> e finalmente <code>0</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Decrementing",
            "id": 74174,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em vez de incrementar a variável contador, nós a decrementamos com <code>i--</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &gt; \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i--) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"26\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"1\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>i--</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "> and >=",
            "id": 74199,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para incluir <code>0</code> ao contar regressivamente, usamos <code>&gt;=</code> em vez de <code>&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &gt;= \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i--) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"0\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&gt;=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Counter variable",
            "id": 74257,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como sabemos que este loop não executa seu bloco de código?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"-71\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &gt; \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i--) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Quando o loop começa, o valor da variável contador é menor que <code>0</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Não podemos dizer se o loop executa seu bloco de código</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Quando o loop começa, o valor da variável contador é menor que <code>0</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Condition",
            "id": 74258,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>O que acontece quando usamos <code>i &gt; 0</code> na condição.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &gt; \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i--) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"1\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">O loop continua enquanto <code>i</code> for maior que <code>0</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">O loop não funciona</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">O loop continua enquanto <code>i</code> for maior que <code>0</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
